cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.CL, cs.PL 

The paper discusses the intersection of reinforcement learning and knowledge representation, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also proposes a logical framework for solving reinforcement learning problems, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The use of answer set semantics and normal logic programs is related to computational linguistics (cs.CL) and programming languages (cs.PL).
